        <p style="font-size:14pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">2018</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">年</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">1~8</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">月，东江流域平均降雨量</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">1289mm</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">，较同期多年（</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">1956~2015</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">年，下同）平均值</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">1447mm</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">偏少</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">11%</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">；其中汛期</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">4~8</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">月降雨量</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">1053mm</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">，占</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">1~8</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">月降雨总量的</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">82%</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">，较同期多年平均值</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">1225mm</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">偏少</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">14%</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">。时间分布上，</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">1</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">月、</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">6</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">月、</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">8</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">月降雨量分别较同期多年平均值偏多</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">292%</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">、</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">23%</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">、</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">55%</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">，</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">2~5</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">月降雨量较同期多年平均值偏少</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">6</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">成左右，</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">7</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">月雨量较常年偏少</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">32%</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">；空间分布上，下游雨量</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">1453mm</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">最大（较同期多年均值偏少</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">3%</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">），其次分别为中游</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">1184mm</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">（较同期多年均值偏少</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">17%</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">）、上游</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">1067mm</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">（较同期多年均值偏少</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">21%</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">）。</span></p>
        <p style="font-size:14pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">2018</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">年</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">1~8</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">月，新丰江水库库区降雨量</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">1237mm</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">，较同期多年（</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">1952~2015</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">年）平均值</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">1516mm</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">偏少</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">18%</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">，其中</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">2~5</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">月及</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">7</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">月雨量偏少</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">4~7</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">成，</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">1</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">月、</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">6</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">月、</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">8</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">月雨量分别较同期多年均值偏多</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">235%</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">、</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">16%</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">、</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">59%</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">；枫树坝水库库区降雨量</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">951mm</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">，较同期多年（</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">1974~2015</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">年）平均值</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">1331mm</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">偏少</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">29%</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">，其中</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">2~5</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">月雨量偏少</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">6~8</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">成，</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">7</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">月雨量较同期多年均值偏少</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">15%</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">，</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">6</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">月雨量与同期多年均值持平，</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">1</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">月、</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">8</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">月雨量分别较同期多年均值偏多</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">245%</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">、</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">15%</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">；白盆珠水库库区降雨量</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">2153mm</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">，较同期多年（</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">1986~2015</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">年）平均值</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">1665mm</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">偏多</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">29%</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">，其中</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">2~5</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">月及</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">7</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">月雨量偏少</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">5~7</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">成，</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">1</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">月、</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">6</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">月、</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">8</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">月雨量分别较多年均值偏多</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">281%</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">、</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">97%</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">、</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">163%</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">。</span></p>
        <p style="font-size:14pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">2018</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">年</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">1~8</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">月，东江干流博罗水文站径流总量</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">108.72</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">亿</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">m</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:9.33pt; vertical-align:super">3</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">，较同期多年（</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">1956~2015</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">年）平均值</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">173.42</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">亿</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">m</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:9.33pt; vertical-align:super">3</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">偏少</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">37%</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">，较去年同期</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">173.45</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">亿</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">m</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:9.33pt; vertical-align:super">3</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">偏少</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">37%</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">。</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">1~8</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">月，新丰江、枫树坝、白盆珠三大水库坝下至博罗站区间平均来水</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">266</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt"> m</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:9.33pt; vertical-align:super">3</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">/s</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">，较同期多年（</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">1986~2015</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">年）平均值</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">461</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">
            m</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:9.33pt; vertical-align:super">3</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">/s</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">偏少</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">42%</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">。</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">1~8</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">月，三大水库总平均入库流量</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">229</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">
            m</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:9.33pt; vertical-align:super">3</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">/s</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">，较同期多年平均值</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">426</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">
            m</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:9.33pt; vertical-align:super">3</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">/s</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">偏少</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">46%</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">。</span></p>
        <p style="font-size:14pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">1~8</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">月，流域降雨较同期多年平均值偏少</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">11%</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">，但由于时间和空间分布不均：</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">1</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">月降雨量较同期多年平均值异常偏多</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">292%</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">（位列</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">1956~2015</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">年期间历史同期第二大，仅次于</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">1983</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">年），</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">2~5</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">月降雨量较同期多年平均值偏少</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">6</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">成左右（</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">2~5</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">月平均降雨量位列</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">1956~2015</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">年期间历史同期第二小，仅次于</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">1963</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">年），虽然</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">6</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">月流域因台风“艾云尼”和西南季风共同影响，当月降雨量较同期多年平均值偏多</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">23%</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">，但</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">7~8</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">月仍有较长时间持续少雨；</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">8</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">月底西枝江流域受季风低压环流影响，</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">8</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">月</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">28</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">日</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">~9</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">月</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">1</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">日，西枝江流域平均降雨量</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">497mm</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">，而东江流域总体平均降雨量为</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">157mm</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">。短时非全流域性的强降雨，并未使东江流域整体偏枯态势得到根本扭转。分别对</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">1~8</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">月及</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">4~8</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">月流域区间平均来水进行评估，来水条件均相当于</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">90%</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">条件下的特枯年景。</span></p>
        <p style="font-size:14pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:27.75pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">截止</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">2018</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">年</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">9</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">月</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">19</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">日</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">8</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">时，三大水库总可调水量</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">46.51</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">亿</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">m</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:9.33pt; vertical-align:super">3</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">，较</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">2017</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">年同期（</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">67.441</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">亿</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">m</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:9.33pt; vertical-align:super">3</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">）少</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">20.94</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">亿</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">m</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:9.33pt; vertical-align:super">3</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">。三大水库蓄水情况见表</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">1-1</span><span style="f