        <p style="margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:10.5pt">&#xa0;</span></p>
        <p style="font-size:12pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:12pt">注：超汛限水位的调洪水量不作为供水可调水量，白盆珠水库汛限水位为</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">76m</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:12pt">，</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:12pt">故</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:12pt">可调水量</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:12pt">按其水位为</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">76m</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:12pt">计算。</span></p>
        <p style="font-size:14pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">汛期</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">4~8</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">月，三大水库总平均入库流量较同期多年平均值偏少</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">46%</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">，汛期三大水库蓄水情况不容乐观。</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">9</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">月</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">19</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">日，新丰江、枫树坝、白盆珠三大水库水位分别为</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">107.28m</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">、</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">152.53m</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">、</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">76.36m</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">，除白盆珠水库以外，新丰江、枫树坝水库仍比今年</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">7</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">月调整后的</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">2018</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">年汛期水量调度目标（争取</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">9</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">月底库水位分别到</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">108m</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">、</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">155m</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">）偏低。</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">2018</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">年</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">9</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">月</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">1</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">日新丰江、枫树坝水库水位分别位列</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">2008</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">年开展水量调度工作以来同期第二、第三低水位。其中，新丰江水库水位仅高于</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">2009</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">年</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">101.37m</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">，枫树坝水库水位仅高于</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">2009</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">年</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">149.13m</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">、</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">2011</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">年</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">150.85m</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">，白盆珠水库水位则为开展水量调度工作以来同期第三高水位（</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">8</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">月</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">28</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">日</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">~9</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">月</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">1</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">日库区平均降雨量为</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">681mm</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">，水库水位短时快速上涨，在</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">9</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">月</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">2</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">日</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">12</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">时达到最高水位</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">79.48m</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">，最大涨幅</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">9.41m</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">），仅次于</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">2013</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">年</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">76.56m</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">、</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">2016</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">年</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">76.22m</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">。</span></p>
        <p style="font-size:14pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">2018</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">年</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">1~8</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">月，流域来水为特枯年景，省东江流域管理局自</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">3</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">月下旬以来，进一步加密与惠州水文分局的会商，根据流域阶段水雨情和三大水库蓄水情况对《广东省东江流域</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">2018</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">年汛期水量调度计划》进行动态调整，全力保障东江中下游供水安全，努力回蓄水库水量。截止</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">2018</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">年</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">9</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">月</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">19</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">日，三大水库总可调水量较汛初（</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">4</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">月</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">1</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">日）增加了</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">6.82</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">亿</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">m</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:9.33pt; vertical-align:super">3</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">，水库蓄水形势相当严峻，今冬明春应充分用好当前水量，灵活应用动态调度机制，力保明春用水安全。</span></p>
        <p style="font-size:15pt; line-height:173%; margin:13pt 0pt 6pt; orphans:0; page-break-after:avoid; page-break-inside:avoid; text-align:justify; text-indent:19.55pt; widows:0"><a name="_Toc210055139"></a><a name="_Toc210983271"></a><a name="_Toc211762703"></a><a name="_Toc237667784"></a><a name="_Toc238116486"></a><a name="_Toc238116540"></a><a name="_Toc238117132"></a><a name="_Toc238117201"></a><a name="_Toc238868834"></a><a name="_Toc523781638"><span style="font-family:楷体_GB2312; font-size:15pt; font-weight:bold">（二）区间及水库来水预测</span><span style="-aw-bookmark-end:_Toc210055139"></span><span style="-aw-bookmark-end:_Toc210983271"></span><span style="-aw-bookmark-end:_Toc211762703"></span><span style="-aw-bookmark-end:_Toc237667784"></span><span style="-aw-bookmark-end:_Toc238116486"></span><span style="-aw-bookmark-end:_Toc238116540"></span><span style="-aw-bookmark-end:_Toc238117132"></span><span style="-aw-bookmark-end:_Toc238117201"></span><span style="-aw-bookmark-end:_Toc238868834"></span></a><span style="width:79.54pt; text-indent:0pt; display:inline-block; -aw-tabstop-align:left; -aw-tabstop-pos:239.1pt"></span></p>
        <p style="font-size:14pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">1~8</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">月，流域降雨时间、空间分布不均，干旱少雨持续时间较长，流域区间来水及水库入库均较同期多年平均值偏少</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">5</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">成左右，今年流域偏枯年景基本已成定局。</span></p>
        <p style="font-size:14pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">根据</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">1</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">~</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">8</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">月水雨情形势，主要采用对比分析、前期降雨与枯水期径流相关、历史演变、数理统计等方法综合分析，推算新丰江、枫树坝水库坝下到河源断面，河源到岭下断面以及岭下、白盆珠水库坝下到博罗断面</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">的区间来水量</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">（区间来水已扣除河道外用水）以及三大水库的来水量。</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">考虑当前及</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">9</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">月的天气形势，分析预测今冬明春枯水期流域来水总体偏枯</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">3~5</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">成。</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">今冬明春枯水期三大水库</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">坝下</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">至博罗断面区间来水、水库入库各月具体预测见表</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">2-1</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">、</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">2-2</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">。</span></p>
