        <p style="font-size:14pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">本期水量调度时间为</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">201</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">8</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">年</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">10</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">月</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">1</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">日至</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">201</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">9</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">年</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">3</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">月</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">31</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">日。根据《广东省东江流域水资源分配方案》要求，遵循高效、合理、节约用水原则，拟定枯水期水量调度目标是确保博罗站的日均流量不小于</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">320m</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:9.33pt; vertical-align:super">3</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">/s</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">。省东江流域管理局将按照实事求是、科学调度的要求，通过动态调度机制，根据对实时水雨情的分析和短期预测，适时调整调度计划，实施较精细化的调度。</span></p>
