        <p style="font-size:14pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">根据《广东省东江西江北江韩江流域水资源管理条例》、《广东省东江流域水资源分配方案》、《广东省东江水量调度管理办法》、《广东省小水电管理办法》和来水预测、水库蓄水情况，通过对三大水库的运行调度和对干流梯级电站、</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">省管</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">取水户的调度管理，合理调配东江流域有限的水资源，保障今冬明春枯水期供水安全。水量调度遵循以下原则：
          </span></p>
        <p style="font-size:14pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">1</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">、水库（东江干流梯级电站）的调度以防洪、供水为主，兼顾发电效益；</span></p>
        <p style="font-size:15pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">2</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">、</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:15pt">优先</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">保障受水区生活、生产用水</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">，</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:15pt">统筹</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">生态环境</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:15pt">以及航运等用水需求；</span></p>
        <p style="font-size:14pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">3</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">、可持续利用和节约保护；</span></p>
        <p style="font-size:15pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">4</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">、</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:15pt">区域水量调度服从流域水量调度，</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">协调上下游、左右岸利益，统筹流域外的调水；</span></p>
        <p style="font-size:14pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">5</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">、水量水质双控制；</span></p>
        <p style="font-size:15pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">6</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">、</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:15pt">常规调度与</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">特殊情况下的动态调度</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">是结合</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">。</span></p>
        <p style="font-size:15pt; line-height:173%; margin:13pt 0pt 6pt; orphans:0; page-break-after:avoid; page-break-inside:avoid; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><a name="_Toc237667787"></a><a name="_Toc238868842"></a><a name="_Toc210983278"></a><a name="_Toc211762708"></a><a name="_Toc238116489"></a><a name="_Toc238116543"></a><a name="_Toc238117204"></a><a name="_Toc238117135"></a><a name="_Toc523781641"></a><a name="_Toc209845496"></a><a name="_Toc210055142"><span style="-aw-bookmark-end:_Toc209845494"></span><span style="-aw-bookmark-end:_Toc210055140"></span><span style="font-family:楷体_GB2312; font-size:15pt; font-weight:bold">（二）</span><span style="-aw-bookmark-end:_Toc209845496"></span></a><span style="font-family:楷体_GB2312; font-size:15pt; font-weight:bold">三大水库调度要求</span><span style="-aw-bookmark-end:_Toc237667787"></span><span style="-aw-bookmark-end:_Toc238868842"></span><span style="-aw-bookmark-end:_Toc210983278"></span><span style="-aw-bookmark-end:_Toc211762708"></span><span style="-aw-bookmark-end:_Toc238116489"></span><span style="-aw-bookmark-end:_Toc238116543"></span><span style="-aw-bookmark-end:_Toc238117204"></span><span style="-aw-bookmark-end:_Toc238117135"></span><span style="-aw-bookmark-end:_Toc523781641"></span></p>
        <p style="font-size:14pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">根据《广东省东江流域水资源分配方案》中各地市水量分配控制指标及各地市上报的今冬明春枯水期取水计划，以及</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">《广东省东江流域新丰江、枫树坝、白盆珠水库供水调度方案（试行）》有关要求，结合</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">今冬明春枯水期的来水预测、</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">区间流量预测分析结果和水量调度目标，今冬明春各月三大水库的日平均控制出库流量见表</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">3-1</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">。为保证下游河道水流情况的稳定，新丰江</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">水库日平均出库流量偏差不得超过表</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">3-1</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">中规定的日均流量的±</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">10%</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">，枫树坝水库日平均出库流量偏差不得超过表</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">3-1</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">中规定的日均流量的±</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">10</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">
