        <p style="font-size:10.5pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="display:none; font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:10.5pt">标</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:10.5pt">注：水质控制目标按粤府办〔</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:10.5pt">2008</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:10.5pt">〕</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:10.5pt">50</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:10.5pt">号文要求。各有关部门应严格控制入河排污量，以达到水质控制目标。</span></p>
        <p style="font-size:15pt; line-height:173%; margin:13pt 0pt 6pt; orphans:0; page-break-after:avoid; page-break-inside:avoid; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><a name="_Toc523781643"><span style="-aw-bookmark-end:_Toc210055143"></span><span style="-aw-bookmark-end:_Toc208914292"></span><span style="font-family:楷体_GB2312; font-size:15pt; font-weight:bold">（四）干流各梯级电站调度要求</span><span style="-aw-bookmark-end:_Toc239563707"></span><span style="-aw-bookmark-end:_Toc237667789"></span><span style="-aw-bookmark-end:_Toc238116491"></span><span style="-aw-bookmark-end:_Toc238116545"></span><span style="-aw-bookmark-end:_Toc238117137"></span><span style="-aw-bookmark-end:_Toc238117206"></span><span style="-aw-bookmark-end:_Toc238868844"></span></a></p>
        <p style="font-size:14pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">根据《广东省小水电管理办法》有关规定，东江干流各已建成运行的梯级电站不得超设计标准（正常蓄水位）运行，应严格将水位控制在正常蓄水位以内，按来多少放多少的原则进行运行调度，不得私自进行拦蓄调节。若因上游汛情或者其他突发性事件导致超正常蓄水位运行的，应采取增大发电流量、开启泄洪闸等措施尽快将水位降至正常蓄水位以下，同时主动报告当地三防部门并报省东江流域管理局备案。</span></p>
        <p style="font-size:14pt; line-height:173%; margin:13pt 0pt 6pt; orphans:0; page-break-after:avoid; page-break-inside:avoid; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">1</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">、东江水利枢纽</span></p>
        <p style="font-size:14pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">正常调度时，东江水利枢纽运行水位保持在</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">10.5m</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">，按来多少放多少的原则进行调度。实施应急调度或临时调度时，省东江流域管理局可在调控三大水库出流的基础上，充分利用枢纽</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">10</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">～</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">10.5m</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">之间的</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">1419</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">万</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">m</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:9.33pt; vertical-align:super">3</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">库容，将枢纽运行水位控制在</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">10</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">～</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">10.5m</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">之间，控制发电下泄流量不小于</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">320m</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:9.33pt; vertical-align:super">3</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">/s</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">，增泄水量视上游来水情况缓慢回蓄补充。东江水利枢纽调蓄能力见表</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">3-4</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">。</span></p>
