        <p style="font-size:14pt; line-height:150%; margin:12pt 0pt 0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:27.8pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">经</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">组织流域</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">内珠江委和省厅发证的河道外</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">取水户</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">（下称“省管</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">取水户</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">”）</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">申报今冬明春枯水期取水计划，按照取水许可管理等有关规定，</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">省管</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">取水户须严格按照</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">《东江流域</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">省管</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">取水户取水计划表》</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">核定下达的取水计划控制取水量（见附表）。若流域出现咸潮上溯等特殊情况需采取应急措施时，各取水户须根据省东江流域管理局下达的应急取水计划严格控制取水量。</span></p>
        <p style="font-size:15pt; line-height:173%; margin:13pt 0pt 6pt; orphans:0; page-break-after:avoid; page-break-inside:avoid; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><a name="_Toc523781646"><span style="font-family:楷体_GB2312; font-size:15pt; font-weight:bold">（七）动态调度</span><span style="-aw-bookmark-end:_Toc238868846"></span><span style="-aw-bookmark-end:_Toc238116547"></span><span style="-aw-bookmark-end:_Toc238116493"></span><span style="-aw-bookmark-end:_Toc238117139"></span><span style="-aw-bookmark-end:_Toc238117208"></span><span style="font-family:楷体_GB2312; font-size:15pt; font-weight:bold">机制</span><span style="-aw-bookmark-end:_Toc239563709"></span></a></p>
        <p style="font-size:14pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:27.75pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">为提高调度的科学性与合理性，节约保护流域水资源，水量调度期间在上述调度计划的基础上，根据《广东省东江水量调度管理办法》中相关规定及实际水雨情采用</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">调整调度计划、</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">动态调度</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">等</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">机制。</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">调度期内，省东江局应加密加强与各有关单位的沟通协调，尤其是加强新丰江水库的动态调度，加强干流梯级电站的监督管理，开展精细准确的联合调度。</span></p>
        <p style="font-size:14pt; line-height:173%; margin:13pt 0pt 6pt; orphans:0; page-break-after:avoid; page-break-inside:avoid; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">1</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">、调度计划调整机制</span></p>
        <p style="font-size:14pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:27.75pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">调度期内，省东江流域管理局会同省水文局惠州水文分局对流域水雨情进行实时分析，若</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">预计未来持续一个月以上</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">博罗站日均流量</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">将比表</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">3-3</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">中的预测值明显偏小且有可能出现小于</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">320</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">m</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:9.33pt; vertical-align:super">3</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">/s</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">或三大水库可调水量与《调度计划》预测的目标偏差较大，由省东江流域管理局提出调整水量调度计划，经征求东江流域有关地级以上市水务局、三大水库工程管理单位等意见后，报省水利厅批准后实施。</span></p>
        <p style="font-size:14pt; line-height:173%; margin:13pt 0pt 6pt; orphans:0; page-break-after:avoid; page-break-inside:avoid; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">2</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">、应急调度机制</span></p>
        <p style="font-size:14pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:27.75pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">当东江流域发生重要控制断面流量小于最小下泄流量、咸潮上溯、水库运行故障、重大水污染事故、干旱缺水、严重塞船等情况，可能危及供水及重要工程设施安全时，按照规定的权限实施应急调度。</span></p>
        <p style="font-size:14pt; line-height:173%; margin:13pt 0pt 6pt; orphans:0; page-break-after:avoid; page-break-inside:avoid; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><a name="_Toc237667791"></a><a name="_Toc238117209"></a><a name="_Toc238117140"></a><a name="_Toc238116548"></a><a name="_Toc238868847"></a><a name="_Toc239563710"></a><a name="_Toc238116494"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">3</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">、临时调度机制</span></a></p>
        <p style="font-size:14pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:28.1pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt; font-weight:normal">因重大节日庆典、体育赛事等重大公共活动需要，经省水利厅同意后，省东江流域管理局和流域有关地级以上市水务局可以实施临时调度。</span></p>
      </div><br style="clear:both; mso-break-type:section-break; page-break-before:always" />
      <div>
        <p style="margin:12pt 0pt; orphans:0; page-break-after:avoid; page-break-inside:avoid; text-align:justify; text-indent:14.8pt; widows:0"><a name="_Toc523781647"><span style="font-family:黑体; font-size:16pt">四、</span><span style="-aw-bookmark-end:_Toc210983280"></span><span style="-aw-bookmark-end:_Toc211762710"></span><span style="-aw-bookmark-end:_Toc237667791"></span><span style="-aw-bookmark-end:_Toc238117209"></span><span style="-aw-bookmark-end:_Toc238117140"></span><span style="-aw-bookmark-end:_Toc238116548"></span><span style="-aw-bookmark-end:_Toc238868847"></span><span style="-aw-bookmark-end:_Toc239563710"></span><span style="-aw-bookmark-end:_Toc238116494"></span><span style="font-family:黑体; font-size:16pt">保障措施</span></a></p>
        <p style="font-size:14pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">流域水资源是一个不可分割的有机整体，东江流域水量调度需要流域上下游各方的齐心协力。各相关部门要统一思想、加强领导、积极配合、落实责任，</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">遵照</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">《广东省东江水量调度管理办法》</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">，</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">服从流域机构的统一调度，严格执行《调度计划》。流域内各地级以上市政府要根据</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">《广东省东江流域水资源分配方案》</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">的要求，负责其行政区域内的取用水总量控制和出境重要控制断面水质目标管理。</span></p>
        <p style="font-size:15pt; line-height:173%; margin:13pt 0pt 6pt; orphans:0; page-break-after:avoid; page-break-inside:avoid; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><a name="_Toc523781648"><span style="font-family:楷体_GB2312; font-size:15pt; font-weight:bold">（一）总体要求</span></a></p>
        <p style="font-size:14pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:18.9pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">东江流域水量调度必须遵循流域管理与区域管理相结合的水资源管理体制的总体要求，坚持科学调度、坚持节约用水，确保今冬明春枯水期东江供水安全，维护东江受水地区经济社会可持续发展。</span></p>
        <p style="font-size:15pt; line-height:173%; margin:13pt 0pt 6pt; orphans:0; page-break-after:avoid; page-break-inside:avoid; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><a name="_Toc523781649"><span style="font-family:楷体_GB2312; font-size:15pt; font-weight:bold">（二）各单位职责</span></a></p>
        <p style="font-size:14pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:20.8pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">在省水利厅的组织、协调、监督和指导下，在省水文局的技术指导下，省东江流域管理局会同各相关部门（单位）具体实施</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">今冬明春</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">枯水期水量调度工作。在工作的开展过程中，省水文局惠州水文分局提供技术支撑，省各有关部门、各地级以上市水务局和水库（电站）管理单位、取水户各司其职、密切配合。各相关部门（单位）按以下的职责落实到位：
          </span></p>
        <p style="font-size:14pt; line-height:173%; margin:13pt 0pt 6pt; orphans:0; page-break-after:avoid; page-break-inside:avoid; text-align:justify; text-indent:21pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">1</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">、省东江流域管理局</span></p>
        <p style="font-size:14pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; text-indent:20.8pt; widows:0"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">具体负责涉及流域内各地级以上市的水量分配、向流域外调水的水量分配和三大水库，东江干流水利枢纽、闸坝、水电站，珠江委和省水利厅审批发放取水许可证的其他取水工程的水量调度工作。</span></p>
        <p style="font-size:14pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 21pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">（</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">1</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">）负责《调度计划》制订及监督实施；</span></p>
        <p style="font-size:14pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 21pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">（</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">2</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">）根据水情变化情况具体负责《调度计划》调整和下达工作；</span></p>
        <p style="font-size:14pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 21pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">（</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">3</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">）负责组织开展相关的监测、巡查、协调工作；</span></p>
        <p style="font-size:14pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 21pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">（</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">4</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">）定期发布《东江流域水量调度情况通报》；</span></p>
        <p style="font-size:14pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 21pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">（</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">5</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">）如发生特大旱情，在省防总的统一指挥下进行水量应急调度；</span></p>
        <p style="font-size:14pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 21pt; orphans:0; text-align:justify; widows:0"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">（</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt">6</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312; font-size:14pt">）如出现突发水污染事件时，按相关规定进行水量应急调度；</span></p>
